data.description: Completely renovated ranch in South Rockdale. Brand new floor coverings throughout, new counters in kitchen, appliances, brushed nickel hardware. Also new light fixtures, doors, and all hardware. New toilets and vanities in both bathrooms. Large finished bonus or rec room adjacent to kitchen 24' by 21'. Also features a large living room with a wood burning stove insert. 1946 square feet heated and cooled. New water heater and vapor barrier in crawl. Large level lot approx. 1 acre with storage building in back yard. Freshly painted inside and out. Absolutely move in ready.  LBP Disclosure in Docs
